boImLkEk74TkKIRmLkEk78TkKILkY==_-115092183&htdbg=on&ie=utf8&s_from=hint_middle)[附近拖车24小时服务热线电话](?user_ip=116&bh=1&hintidx=9&query=%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E6%8B%96%E8%BD%A624%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%83%AD%E7%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D&w=01020600&sessiontime=1774152822887&interation=&interV=kKIOkrELjbkRmLkElbkTkKIMkrELjboImLkEk74TkKIRmLkEk78TkKILkY==_-115092183&htdbg=on&ie=utf8&s_from=hint_middle)\n\n### [广西组织开展县域充换电设施补短板试点 - 今日头条](/link?url=hedJjaC291PD0T3DYzJqFDoBhFbePHvernilvTOuwmnGWE5vZ-OH3KmZdSp_gzmjgSCN38NLAU4.)\n根据中央政策规定,2024—2026年为充换电设施补短板试点期,其中2024年广西获得充换电设施补短板县域数量2个,后续试点工作视试点开展情况再另行确定。\n [今日头条 https://www.toutiao.com/a... 2024-05-04](/link?url=hedJjaC291PD0T3DYzJqFDoBhFbePHvernilvTOuwmnGWE5vZ-OH3KmZdSp_gzmjgSCN38NLAU4.)\n\n[广西换电 充电 2026 -看看ima怎么说腾讯ima-AI工作台 基于知识库问答更精准去试试](https://ima.qq.com/?type=search&launchChannel=10000031&extraInfo=%7B%22launchChannel%22:%2210000031%22%7D&question=%E5%B9%BF%E8%A5%BF%E6%8D%A2%E7%94%B5%20%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%202026)\n\n### [解读|广西城市更新五年行动充电桩专项:2000个小区全覆盖、配...](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1774152823&ver=6613&signature=2YocNEW-k1SaSVW2BkHHLI-MN2ZfbYZ7l6Drv2S6-kf3OGwjV0hlYJ*I-pblLUPJq8O3k6uTeVTLNK6jTUeCE-kw9vkyE7zUHtA0CpIA4umAz4ZMhXm12kL4*fARCfpO&new=1)\n\n http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1774152823&ver=6613&signature=2YocNEW-k1SaSVW2BkHHLI-MN2ZfbYZ7l6Drv2S6-kf3OGwjV0hlYJ*I-pblLUPJq8O3k6uTeVTLNK6jTUeCE-kw9vkyE7zUHtA0CpIA4umAz4ZMhXm12kL4*fARCfpO&new=1\n\n2026年3月,广西正式印发《广西持续推进城市更新五年行动方案(2026—2030年)》(以下简称《方案》),将充电桩建设纳入城市更新核心民生任务,与老旧小区改造、完整社区建设、城市基础设施升级深度绑定.\n\n[腾讯网http://mp.weixin.qq.com/c...4天前](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1774152823&ver=6613&signature=2YocNEW-k1SaSVW2BkHHLI-MN2ZfbYZ7l6Drv2S6-kf3OGwjV0hlYJ*I-pblLUPJq8O3k6uTeVTLNK6jTUeCE-kw9vkyE7zUHtA0CpIA4umAz4ZMhXm12kL4*fARCfpO&new=1)\n\n### [县域充换电设施补短板试点开展情况及首批67个试点县名单_支持_政策...](/link?url=hedJjaC291Ok-E9WTygIKqZt6DizBOEjkUjiKB1DSQkEPQ0Rp1dIQg..)\n\n /link?url=hedJjaC291Ok-E9WTygIKqZt6DizBOEjkUjiKB1DSQkEPQ0Rp1dIQg..\n\n 计划持续至2026年。以